What you need to know:

He has over the past few years developed a penchant for Kenyan classic car events which include the iconic nine-day East African Safari Classic Rally, and indeed, the Mini Classics.Melvyn Evans Motorsport will supply a New VW Polo R5 to Minti Motorsport which will run in the United Arabs Emirates, Oman Rally Championships, selected African Rally Championship and indeed Kenya’s WRC event. 